description: Whenever you need a sweet treat in your day, enjoy a pouch of Black Forest Juicy Center Fruity Medleys Fruit Flavored Snacks. Made with real fruit juice and containing 100% of your daily value of vitamin C, this is a treat you'll feel good about.
